Nos unimos a Mia Khalifa en su preparación para la Milan Fashion Week Otoño-Invierno 2024.¡Conoce todos los detalles y su estilo único en este evento icónico! ✨

PHRESH OUT THE RUNWAY @avellano !!!!!! Hunter green Latex dress and trench of my DREAMS!!! Thank you @arthuravellano I’m so honored to slither myself into one of your pieces, let alone one STRAIGHT FROM THE SHOW! Congratulations on this iconic collection!

MUGLERRRRRRRR!!!!! What a SHOW, what a COLLECTION!!!! Thank you so much for having me, I’m so honored to have been there in person to see this insane presentation, I can’t believe I saw Mona and Yasmin stomp by me tonight. Ending my PFW on the highest note possible🥹 thank you @saraburnstudio and @coralilliana for the best week- I love you🖤

What's it like behind the scenes at fashion week? Model and entrepreneur Mia Khalifa (@MiaKhalifa) touched down in Paris for the Acne Studios (@acnestudios) show. Come along as she gets ready for #ParisFashionWeek2024.

I went to the @schiaparelli show!!!!!!! I didn’t go in… but I went!🥹🥲 missed the doors shutting by 3 minutes because of a zipper malfunction, but because of my hero @saraburnstudio I was still able to wear my absolute dream dress and feel like a Lebanese queen last night. Thank you @badra_amart for inviting me to be your guest, I am so grateful for the opportunity and even more grateful in life to be able to wear and own these works of art. Congratulations @danielroseberry and the entire atelier team, the photos I saw from this collection were STUNNING!!! AND THE BIGGEST THANK YOU TO @isamayabeauty TEAM FOR TURNING ME INTO @haifawehbe FOR THE NIGHT!!!

The dream team from @isamayabeauty on this insane glam for the @schiaparelli show. Thank you my queen @isamayaffrench for this golden gift - it didn’t leave my hand all night 💛♥️ I’ll tell you guys the story of how I didn’t actually make it tomorrow🥹
TEARSSSSS over this presentation!!!!! THANK YOU @off____white for having me and DRESSING me!!! Congratulations @ibkamara and your entire team, this collection will go down in history💙🖤

I feel so lucky to be a part of the @acnestudios family! This dress and trench are my own and I’ve been dying to wear them, everything this brand does speaks to me on an emotional level, I love you guys so much CONGRATULATIONS on the incredible collection, I’m going to need to pre-order every shoe and fur coat that went down that runway!

wearing CUSTOM NOT EVEN OFF THE RUNWAY YET @estermanas AaaahhhhHhHhh!!! The girl power was so strong in the building tonight, this brand means so much to me as a woman- the way I feel in it and the way seeing it on other beautiful bodies makes me feel is so special. I adore you Ester and Balthazar, congratulations on the incredible presentation, thank you for having me and for dressing me I’m so honored🥹🩶
